Preheat the grill to high. Put the chicken in a large bowl.Mix together the yoghurt, curry powder, garlic, ginger and lime juice. Season with salt and pepper, then spoon over the chicken and mix well.Thread the chicken and tomatoes alternately onto metal skewers and place under the grill for 6â€“8 minutes, turning once, halfway through cooking or until lightly charred at the edges and cooked through.Serve with the chopped cucumber, mint and red onion salad and pitta bread.